data.description: Needs some TLC to bring this home back to its full potential. 2 Bedroom,2 Bathroom Manufactured Home located just off Marina Boulevard. Sits on top of the hill so you have some great views. Super close to the entertainment of the Colorado River and Laughlin casinos. Interior features include breakfast bar, dining area, laundry/utility room and a single car garage/storage off the back. Exterior has full length covered patio in front with sun screen; offers the spectacular view of the west mountains and the Arizona sunset.
